name: Oh Well (Electric Triangle Studios)
description:
Game Description:

You're trying to get all the way to the bottom of the well, think you can? It may seem easy until you see what lurks in the deep well waters... There will be obstacles and creatures lurking, who knows what sits at the bottom?

Controls:

Arrow Keys/ASD

Additional Details:

Made within 48 hours for the Rider University Game Jam.
